{"id": 682, "genre": 1001, "title": "当他们在说气质的时候你看到了什么？", "description": "你的朋友圈被“主要看气质”刷屏了吗？说起来，朋友圈的气质主要分为“主要看滤镜”、“主要看化妆”和“主要看智商”三种。", "record_count": 3469, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194309T08pAfHOUhL2iNnx.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-12-07T10:45:15Z", "options": [{"id": 32256, "content": "帅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144759}, {"id": 32512, "content": "绿茶婊又要刷屏了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343071}, {"id": 32257, "content": "气质＝脸＝自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294749}, {"id": 32513, "content": "其实根本不知道这是个什么东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 96467}, {"id": 32259, "content": "谜一样的自信", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192831MBDwNYoS0ngtKjJV.jpg", "praise_count": 654, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 342174}, {"id": 32260, "content": "都是什么鬼", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168028}, {"id": 32516, "content": "哎，不參與。", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211816dfAwMhe71IQVEJLs.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321477}, {"id": 32261, "content": "怎么都挺丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334958}, {"id": 32517, "content": "没有脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345202}, {"id": 32262, "content": "笼罩着光芒…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323525}, {"id": 32264, "content": "我要停用朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301218}, {"id": 32267, "content": "从没在公共社交台上发过自拍。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343357}, {"id": 32779, "content": "找个借口各种秀呗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346455}, {"id": 32268, "content": "说是不发照片要给红包就发了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 338793}, {"id": 33036, "content": "挺无聊的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347924}, {"id": 32269, "content": "说是不发照片就得给5.21元的红包，所以我就发了照片。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 338793}, {"id": 32270, "content": "丑逼看气质，美人看颜值", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 314188}, {"id": 32271, "content": "给许久未发自拍的。或者从没发过自拍的找一个洋气的借口！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343308}, {"id": 32273, "content": "人丑多作怪", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343371}, {"id": 33298, "content": "绿茶婊...心机婊...炫富婊...装逼男...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349616}, {"id": 32276, "content": "然而并没有参与", "image": null, "praise_count": 450, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 312548}, {"id": 32277, "content": "丑～～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334473}, {"id": 32278, "content": "主要看勇气", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287315}, {"id": 32279, "content": "看看大家近来都长变样没", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 309180}, {"id": 32280, "content": "那就没什么好看的了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343424}, {"id": 32537, "content": "颜值低的而有气质的人=有魅力，颜值高的人当然也是一种气质=有魅力。颜值低还没气质的人，却硬要发个图说主要看气质=这人有自信啊。所以都是可以的！我心好，所以看到的都是别人好的地方！你们嘲讽这，嘲笑那的，都是一定程度上的思想扭曲。所以我心好=有魅力。", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211816PagqdDJQk5o4eshI.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343363}, {"id": 32283, "content": "主要看脸蛋和主要看身材的基本没参加……", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200758WRMj2DOpb6Zn3Yql.jpg", "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307085}, {"id": 32285, "content": "无所谓  whatever ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241588}, {"id": 32546, "content": "谜一样的自信", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335373}, {"id": 32292, "content": "有什么卵用？？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 315613}, {"id": 32293, "content": "娱乐至死", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343220}, {"id": 32549, "content": "说你有气质，只是敷衍你吧了，因为你真的没有什莫优点可以赞美了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345332}, {"id": 32294, "content": "说你有气质，只是为你不漂亮的外表找个漂亮的借口而已。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343578}, {"id": 32295, "content": "看气质是因为丑。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162956}, {"id": 32298, "content": "都闲的蛋疼......", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330198}, {"id": 32299, "content": "气质是什么?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 300029}, {"id": 32300, "content": "看气质首先得读书", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235433}, {"id": 32301, "content": "没对焦的存照", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493}, {"id": 33325, "content": "明知山有虎 偏向虎山行……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349719}, {"id": 32303, "content": "不美你说话", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211814TsJfKdhlV4aCG3uR.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343683}, {"id": 32304, "content": "看不出来", "image": "img/option/option/2016060521192252BtoWKSDei4cQOL.jpg", "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323074}, {"id": 32307, "content": "看到的全是赵四", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334466}, {"id": 33075, "content": "新一代的微商", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 230595}, {"id": 32308, "content": "缺什么发什么…", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341717}, {"id": 32821, "content": "主要看弱智。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262017}, {"id": 32310, "content": "不加班了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330000}, {"id": 32311, "content": "是一种气势", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343739}, {"id": 32312, "content": "还是主要看脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 342552}, {"id": 32314, "content": "长得丑的人才看气质，长得好看脸就足够了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265401}, {"id": 32570, "content": "我只静静微笑不说话", "image": "img/option/option/2016060521181668FoYdOBn0l1PMbf.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345367}]}